<plot>Set amidst the whimsical world of a children's pizza palace/video game arcade, Play Land tells the touching tale of Mark and Darryl. They are two estranged brothers (early 30's) who enter this zany land of pizza and prizes. They hope to commit the ultimate heist: stealing the coveted, prize robot that eluded their grasp since childhood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?435077</url></doc>
